message.body: Hey there! It Skylar
hey how u doin?
Good! Just playing video games. What are you up to?
Sry I fell asleep last night. Had to get up extra early for work this week
Hey sorry I lost my phone and just found it again haha. How are you??
I'm doing good just got home from gym. What r u up too?
Just playing some Guild wars 2 haha
Is that Xbox?
No it's on my Mac haha
What's Ur fav game?
Guild wars 2 haha
Nice. I've never played one of those type games
So u live in phoenixville?
Yeah during the school year. I'm home for the summer. I'll be back in phoenixville in August
Where's home?
Middletown NY
Oh wow. R u there now?
Yeah I hate it here :(
How far away is it?
Like 3 hours. ( sorry thought my text sent
Oh wow that's a hike! I was tryna collab on some videos!
What do you want to do?? Like what effects did you have in mind for your music videos??
I wanna do whatever is feasible. I dun really know the possibilities.
Well let me know, I can look up tutorials and learn pretty fast on whatever you want done
So u are in a band as well??
Yeah I was. But my contract is up so now I'm done
What's that mean Ur contract was up??
Oh it a school organized group and people audition every year and get a huge scholarship. It's an 18 month contract
U play bass?
Yep! Absolutely love it
What kinda music was Ur band?
We did Chritian music. But we put on concerts 3 times outbid the year and we did popular covers of songs like Paramore and stuff
I take it u are very religious??
No not at all. Haha I'm not one of those weird Christians you see on TV. What I have is different.
What do u have?
What I have is a relationship with God. I don't shove Jesus down people's throats, I don't tell people they're going to hell, nor do I judge anyone. I ju
st love God an love people. Hope you don't think that's weird haha
Haha u can believe whatever u like. Not my place to judge either. So what kinda music do u listen too??
I listen to anything really. I really like bands like Paranore and 30 Seconds to Mars and bands alike
I wanna get more into paramore. So what u doin for the summer?
Old Paramors before they broke up, we're amazing. Now they're just ok. Ad this summer I was supposed to intern but it fell through so ill probably just work
You just have one more yr of college??
Yeah I was supposed to graduate this year but I am just a tad behind
Where u wanna live after graduation?
I want to stay in Phoenixville for a bit. Then I don't know where. It's always been a dream to live in NYC
Ha that'll be a big change from Middletown! U ever been to philly?
Yeah I have actually! I like it there
Yea that's where I live. Center city
How is it there?
I love it. I live with a roommate but we live in a nice apartment in an awesome area
How is living in an apartment on your own? My mom thinks its impossible at my age but I think otherwise
How old r u? Who do u live with in phoenixville
I'm 21 and I plan on renting an apartment this fall
Where were u living? Dorm?
Yeah on campus. I hated it
How come??
Because I started getting annoyed living on campus. People annoyed me and there wasn't a lot of freedom
What race r u?
Puerto Rican and a quarter Italian
Do u speak Spanish?
Very little haha
Damn Ur parents slack in!!
Haha tell me bout it! Haha
Which parent is which?
My mom is full Puerto Rican and my dad is half Puerto Rican half Italian
Ahh u have no excuses! How come they didn't teach u? Do u have siblings?
I just know a few words, I took Spanish in high school but forgot it all now. Haha and I have an older brother
So do u do any filming as well??
Sometimes, I haven't lately due to my other projects. I wanted to do sole stuff this summer for fun
What sole projects do u wanna do
I like doing anything really. Music videos, short films, but I actually wanted to get into documentaries
What do u shoot with??
Just a simple Nikon DSLR. I really want a Canon mark 2
Yea I have a Nikon d5100...want that canon 7d or 5d too!!
They're so amazing!!!!
Yea that price ain't amazing though. Bout to suck it up and buy one though
I don't have the money at all haha
Mark ii way more expensive than 7d though... what u wanna make docs abt?
Anything really. I've just always wanted to do one
u have to do lots of research and know Ur stuff! I was thinking bout doing one on freedom of internet once
Yeah it'll be a lot of work but I want the experience under my belt. Ie always wanted to do a documentary on third world living like in the slums of India
U ever see born into brothels?
That sounds so familiar, bit I don't think I've seen it
You should watch it! Won an Oscar few years back
I'll look for it later tonight! I love a good documentary
Yeah real depressing though
Aww I bet :( Is it set in India?
Yeah bout the kids who are born by prostitutes
Aww :( that's terrible
Yep what's Ur fav movie??
I have a ton but I really love The Lord of the Rings series. I just love that kind of fantasy world.
Ah u like fantasy? Goes with the video games. U like anime?
Oh my gosh I used to be a total anime nerd in high school lol
Yeah I love anime. What shows did u like?
Inuyasha, dragon ball Z, fruits baskets, gundam
Cowboy bebop prob my favorite and dbz of course
I've never actually watched cowboy bebop but I did see the movie and I really liked it
I have the entire series if u ever wanna watch!
That would be sweet!!!
I guess u can't meet up til August tho huh?
Yeah unfortunately :( I don't have a car or anything
Ur parents drive u back to school in fall?
Very rarely. Me and my brother drive together
He goes to school there too?
Yeah we are both digital media majors
U guys close??
Not really, he usually annoys me all the time haha
He's younger?
No he's older haha
He in grad school?
No he's actually really behind because community college screwed him up so he's actually a year behind me
I see. That stinks
